      h6 Bust
      p Measure around the fullest part of your bust

      h6 Waist
      p Measure around your natural waistline. 

      h6 Hips
      p Measure 20cm below your waistline at the fullest part of your hips.

      h6 Skirt Length
      p Stand with your heels together, keep the tape straight and perpendicular to the floor. Measure from your natural waistline.
